description:
Been a while since we just sat down and talked (sorry If I got a little rambly). Wanted to talk about an important topic. Stay positive, hold on to the light when it becomes dark all around you. If you or anyone you know is suffering from depression please talk to someone.

https://suicidepreventionlifeline.org/

Jesus said to love one another and that we should be servants to each other, so I would ask that you all do that in the comment section. That means more to me than anything. Thank you.

~CK
